        <name xml:lang="en">Phenol</name>
        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">The remaining amount of unreacted phenol (4.8 % of the input) is assumed to leave the production process with the wastewater. Further it is assumed that this wastewater is treated in a internal wastewater plant. The removal efficiency for phenol is assumed with 90%. The carbon contained in the removed phenol is accounted as CO2 emissions to air.</comment>
